      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2006/01/new-year-new-york/#comment-2866"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2006-02-11T00:17:00-05:00">Saturday, February 11, 2006 at 12:17 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>AJ, &#8220;awesome&#8221; is really the right word for this salad.  So glad to hear that you tried it and approve!</p>
